  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Where am I? Who am I?\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neu quietly awakened in his ancient temple to fulfill the terms of an agreement he no longer remembers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, what was this agreement?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Neu on his quest to rediscover himself and his memories. Challenge the immortal guardians of the realm of Aytol, which has fallen into chaos, and enter an eternal struggle to cleanse their souls from corruption.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Remember your past. Choose your destiny. Fight the chaos!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/fff1f0374d1f4e712a4d6b1dc128d999.poster.avif?t=1746093900\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/fff1f0374d1f4e712a4d6b1dc128d999.webm?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/fff1f0374d1f4e712a4d6b1dc128d999.mp4?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wander Through Mysterious Lands:</strong> Are you ready to get lost in the mystical realm of Aytol?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/1808c5d955af603267f758e3726d7672.poster.avif?t=1746093900\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/1808c5d955af603267f758e3726d7672.webm?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/1808c5d955af603267f758e3726d7672.mp4?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face Powerful Bosses:</strong> Confront the mighty godlings of the god Kaira. Discover how they move, avoid their deadly attacks, and defeat them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/755bdcc453a1ae82651c4f8136abe6de.poster.avif?t=1746093900\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/755bdcc453a1ae82651c4f8136abe6de.webm?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/755bdcc453a1ae82651c4f8136abe6de.mp4?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadly Battles:</strong> Test your patience. As Neu, don’t let the grotesque creatures consume you. In this cursed land where death is forbidden, even if you fall, you will rise again from your balbal grave.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/805616444c5b7246cd290aae38c402f6.poster.avif?t=1746093900\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/805616444c5b7246cd290aae38c402f6.webm?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/805616444c5b7246cd290aae38c402f6.mp4?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn and Improve:</strong> Gain new abilities and use them however you like. Find mystical items waiting to be discovered and strengthen Neu’s body.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/091dcdd6ee3d504c9ebafbcef17ad54b.poster.avif?t=1746093900\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/091dcdd6ee3d504c9ebafbcef17ad54b.webm?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745050/extras/091dcdd6ee3d504c9ebafbcef17ad54b.mp4?t=1746093900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the Story’s Hidden Layers:</strong> Help Neu regain his memory and explore the story.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy Pixel Art Graphics and Animations:</strong> Delight in carefully crafted pixel art graphics and smooth animations.</p></li></ul>",
